data.description: It's a dream for entertaining both inside and outside...This kitchen has stainless steel appliances, a deep sink, tile floor and large center island. The full bath has lots of vanity and storage space. The home has an electric fireplace with stone surrounding it, wood floors in the living room and is tastefully decorated throughout. There are two bedrooms up with closets and either a 3rd bedroom on the 1st floor or a den. The large, enclosed porch adds to living space for three seasons. Outside a deck leads to the large L shaped yard with a garden shed.
